  • Field Details

    • adjMatrix

      protected double[][] adjMatrix
      Adjacency matrix. adjMatrix[i][j] means weight from i-th to j-th vertex. There are 4 posibilities: POSITIVE_INFINITY (weight is unknow), 0 (weight from i-th to i-th vertex), NaN (if vertex is removed), any other value - valid weight.

    • nvertices

      protected int nvertices
      Number of vertices.

      public Integer addVertex(Integer v)

      Inserted vertex.

    • removeVertex

      public Integer removeVertex(Integer v)

      Removed vertex.
